I'm a young man who likes Leo Aril's work.
Which of your achievements in the federation do you consider the greatest?
That I was part of the most famous era of the national team between 1988 and 1995, and that in the early 1990s, the BSN National League had 17 teams in one season.
What didn't you prove?
